 and dapper that you’ve been searching far and wide for with four different fits — slim regular classic and modern — in each of variousstyled slacks every guy can find the style they strive for in the size that fits after all different guys like different styles and dress pants can be the difference maker to any outfit keep it casual but classy when you pick up a pair of chinos which give a perfect professional look while keeping a laidback approach they show that you’re trendy but don’t take fashion too serious have an oldschool business style with a modern touch then perry ellis portfolio pleated or doublepleated pants are the exact trouser you’re looking for incorporating a noniron wrinklefree finish into a style that’s never out of season you can pay homage to the timeless looks of yesteryear while impressing everyone at the office skip the dry cleaner because our trousers are machine washable which means they’re an excellent wardrobe addition for the onthego businessman headed to prom homecoming formal or just a blacktie event arrive in style when you pair your pants with suit separates to make a threepiece suit that’s sure to make you shine add a tie and pocket square to include a pop of color into your wardrobe or just go for the minimalist look in the office or on the weekend when you pair your dress pants with a polo or knit with fabrications like sharkskin herringbone heather chambray melange bengaline and linen in slim fit to big  tall you’re assured to find the style you’re looking for in the fit you deserve sort by best matches top rated price high to low price low to high default availability top sellers new arrivals top seller  avail go items per page   view all  go    compare up to  products       compare items clear all travel luxe very slim twill dress pant  compare travel luxe very slim twill dress pant kfb noniron travel luxe subtle check pant  compare noniron travel luxe subtle check pant cmbps modern fit sharkskin pleated dress pant  compare mo